.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: ebony, white, azure, orange, amber
Nationality: french, pakistani, brazilian, egyptian, mexican
Cigar: oliveros, davidoff, blend, tiparillo, swisher
Beverage: mirinda, iced-tea, sprite, fanta, almond-milk
Pet: rat, snake, frog, cat, hamster

1. Nationality:french == Color:ebony
2. Nationality:pakistani == Pet:rat
3. Beverage:mirinda == Color:white
4. Nationality:brazilian == Beverage:iced-tea
5. Color:white is to the right of Color:azure
6. Cigar:oliveros == Pet:hamster
7. Cigar:davidoff == Color:orange
8. Beverage:sprite is in the middle
9. Nationality:egyptian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:snake
11. Cigar:davidoff is to the left or right of Pet:cat
12. Cigar:tiparillo == Beverage:fanta
13. Nationality:mexican == Cigar:swisher
14. Nationality:egyptian is to the left or right of Color:amber

